														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4332715">
									

<p>IT'S UP! \o/</p>
<p>I have to say, Ad Astra is an absolute BLAST to read and contribute to! This is, of course, due to the solid writing and diligence on the part of its many contributors; the wealth of science fiction/space opera concepts and narratives to choose from; and the hard work of Nat for arranging everything and tying it all together, and acting as an ever-present source of ideas and feedback along the way. It's <em>really</em> thrilling to see this up and I can't wait to see what people contribute in the future.</p>
<p>+1 <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">to infinity and beyond</span> to the stars through hardship!</p>

							</div>

